@Procurement
Feature: Chemical, Proppant and Email Setup

    
    
@setUpProcurement    
Scenario: Verify user can navigate to Procurement module 
    Given the user clicks on Procurement sidebar
    
Scenario: Addition of the PO for the first chemical
    When the user click on the create new po button
Scenario: Job Number Selection    
    And the user select the job number from the job number dropdown
Scenario: Verify PO number can be entered for first chemical vendor    
    And the user enters PONumber for first chemical vendor into the PO Number input field 
Scenario: Verify first chemical vendor can be selected    
    And the user selects first chemical vendor from the vendor dropdown
Scenario: First Chemical Selection    
    And the user select the first chemical from the chemical item dropdown
    And the user enter the po quantity for first chemical
    And the user click on the plus icon to add chemical
Scenario: Verify second chemical can be selected and po quantity can be added    
    And the user select the second chemical and provide the po quantity
    And the user click on the plus icon for second time
Scenario: Verify third chemical can be selected and po quantity can be added    
    And the user select the third chemical and provide the po quantity    
    And the user click on the plus icon for third time
Scenario: Verify fourth chemical can be selected and po quantity can be added    
    And the user select the fourth chemical and provide the po quantity
    And the user click on the plus icon for fourth time
Scenario: Verify fifth chemical can be selected and po quantity can be added    
    And the user select the fifth chemical and provide the po quantity
    And the user click on the plus icon for fifth time
Scenario: Verify sixth chemical can be selected and po quantity can be added    
    And the user select the sixth chemical and provide the po quantity
    And the user click on the plus icon for sixth time
    And the user select the seventh chemical and provide the po quantity
    And the user click on the Add button to add procurement
    
